N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6404.11 - Cultural services contract

State Regulations

Every applicant granted financial assistance shall be
required to execute a cultural services contract with the council. The
procedures for entering into a cultural services contract are described in
detail in the program guidelines. Notes
